texts.content: {"text":"3. Yarmida yoki undan bir oz qisqarog`ida \n(bedor bo`l).","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"4. Yoki u(yarim)ga yana qo`sh va \nQur'onni tartil bilan tilovat qil.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"6. Albatta, kechki ibodat ko`proq muvofiq kelur va qiroati to`g`riroq bo`lur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,77]}]}

{"text":"8. Va Robbingning ismini zikr et va \nUning ibodatiga butunlay ajralib chiq.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,75]}]}

{"text":"9. U mashriqu mag`ribning Robbidir. \nUndan o`zga ibodatga sazovor iloh yo`q. \nBas, Uni o`zingga vakil qil.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,106]}]}

{"text":"10. Va ularning gaplariga sabr qil va ulardan chiroyli chetlash-la chetlab tur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,79]}]}

{"text":"11. Ahli ne'mat bo`lgan yolg`onga chiqaruvchilarni O`zimga qo`yib qo`y va \nularga ozgina muhlat ber.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,100]}]}

{"text":"14. Bir kundaki, unda yeru tog`lar larzaga keladi va tog`lar oquvchi qumtepalarga aylanadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,91]}]}

{"text":"15. Albatta, Biz sizlarga, xuddi Fir'avnga Rasul yuborganimizdek, siz haqingizda guvohlik beruvchi Rasulni yubordik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,116]}]}

{"text":"16. Bas, Fir'avn Rasulga osiy bo`ldi va Biz uni shiddatli azob bilan tutdik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"17. Agar kofir bo`lsalaringiz, bolalarning sochini oqartirib yuboradigan kundan qanday saqlanursiz?!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,100]}]}

{"text":"18. Unda osmon parchalanuvchidir, \nU zotning va'dasi amalga oshadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,68]}]}

{"text":"19. Albatta, bular eslatmadir, \nKim xohlasa, o`z Robbi tomon yo`l oladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,73]}]}

{"text":"20. Albatta, Robbing seni kechaning uchdan ikkisidan ozrog`ini, yo yarmini, yo uchdan birini qoim bo`lib \no`tkazayotganingni va sen bilan birga bo`lganlardan ham bir toifa (shundoq qilayotganlarini) biladir. \nVa Alloh kechayu kunduzni O`zi o`lchaydir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,252]}]}

{"text":"U sizlar hech chiday olmasligingizni bilib, \nsizlarga (engillikni) qaytardi. Bas (endi), \nQur'ondan muyassar bo`lganicha o`qinglar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,132]}]}

{"text":"Sizlardan kelajakda kasallar bo`lishini ham bildi. Boshqalar Yer yuzida yurib, Allohning fazlini axtarishini, yana boshqalar esa, Allohning yo`lida jihod qilishlarini (ham bildi). Bas, undan muyassar bo`lganicha \nqiroat qilinglar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,231]}]}

{"text":"Va namozni qoim qilinglar, zakot beringlar va \nAllohga yaxshi qarz beringlar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,78]}]}

{"text":"O`zingiz uchun nima yaxshilik qilgan bo`lsangiz, Allohning huzurida undan yaxshirog`ini va ulkanroq ajrni toparsizlar. Allohga istig`for aytinglar. Albatta, Alloh mag`firat qiluvchi va rahmdildir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,196]}]}
